{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <p>你是否經常忘記重要的生日、假期、考試或截止日期呢？Countdown Widget 這款應用程式，能有效解決您生活中的時間管理難題，讓您輕鬆掌握每一個關鍵時刻，現在終生版限時免費下載，無論是忙碌的學生、專業人士，或是任何希望更有條理地安排生活的人，都能透過它來追蹤並提醒生命中的大小事，告別遺憾，迎接從容。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/460x460bb-75-2.webp\" alt=\"限時免費\">\n    <h2>一目了然追蹤所有重要日子</h2>\n    <p>Countdown Widget 讓您能以最簡潔直觀的方式管理所有即將到來的事件，無廣告干擾，更無需註冊帳號，離線也能完整使用，您可以為每個事件新增表情符號或照片，透過顏色編碼快速辨識，無論是生日、假期、考試、工作截止日，甚至是健身目標或帳單繳費，都能精準掌握，讓生活井然有序。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1320x2868bb-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1320x2868bb-1-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1320x2868bb-2-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1320x2868bb-3-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/2064x2752bb-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/2064x2752bb-1-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <h2>限時免費領取終生版</h2>\n    <p>Countdown Widget 終生版限時免費中，用戶先建立一個提示後，在主介面可找到升級，看到 Lifetime 價格顯示為 $0，即可免費獲得此 App 的終生版本授權。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/IMG_3082-473x1024.webp\" alt=\"IMG 3082\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/IMG_3083-473x1024.webp\" alt=\"IMG 3083\">\n    <ul>\n      <li>應用名稱：Countdown Widget</li>\n      <li>應用類別：Utilities</li>\n      <li>下載位置：App Store</li>\n    </ul>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-01T08:04:26.299592+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":457,"images":9,"source":"New MobileLife","fallback":"none"}}